{"tid":2314569,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"西貢單車手致命車禍　涉事消防車司機被捕 現正被扣留調查","createTime":"2020-12-06T15:39:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T01:16:21.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"64f1ea8710800b7362b3d5468da8a831907f87b9","tid":2314569,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T15:39:25.000Z","msg":"警方調查西貢白沙灣下午發生的致命交通意外，事件中一名60歲外籍男子死亡。涉案54歲消防車司機涉嫌危險駕駛導致他人死亡被捕，現正被扣留調查。<br />\n<br />\n事發於下午約1時45分，意外涉及一輛消防車、一輛單車和一輛私家車。其中踏單車的外籍男子被捲入消防車車底，救出時昏迷，送往將軍澳醫院，最終傷重不治，私家車男司機亦報稱不適送院。<br />\n<br />\n消防處對事件深表遺憾，發言人說，已經派員嘗試接觸死者家屬，希望提供一切可行的協助，並會全面協助警方調查，並提供一切所需資料。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1563882-20201206.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1563882-20201206.htm&d=PkQR3zmsNSOm8whbchxq2pFDRn80AWZfiUxX1c6OkmY%3D&h=d1c50459\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1563882-20201206.htm&h=8c81cb89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1563882-20201206.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8e2bc0fcaa7273c7ea096019b822a103b9a70209","tid":2314569,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T15:54:58.000Z","msg":"除非你係黨軍"},{"pid":"994cabfb90afc566c8393509da90bc9b7528a1cd","tid":2314569,"uid":138964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T15:56:38.000Z","msg":"一點四十五西貢西斜呀<br />\n體諒下ok?"},{"pid":"7f7175296f2696a1ef902b7cb6015c8439061406","tid":2314569,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"994cabfb90afc566c8393509da90bc9b7528a1cd","tid":2314569,"uid":138964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T15:56:38.000Z","msg":"一點四十五西貢西斜呀<br />\n體諒下ok?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T15:58:19.000Z","msg":"鳩屈話有暴徒玩雷射槍雷射炮激光槍乜乜乜咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" clas